SELECT
usercode,
date_format( attdate, '%Y-%m-01' ) MONTH,
sum( CASE WHEN onduty_type = '1' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) latetimes,
sum( CASE WHEN offduty_type = '3' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) overtimes1,
sum( CASE WHEN onduty_type = '3' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) overtimes2,
sum( CASE WHEN offduty_type = '2' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) leavetimes,
sum( absenceDay ) AS absencetimes,
sum( lateTime ) AS lateduration,
sum( overtimeTime ) AS overtimelength,
sum( leaveEarlyTime ) AS leavetduration,
sum( CASE WHEN offduty_type NOT IN ( '4', '5' ) THEN 0.5 ELSE 0 END ) workdays1,
sum( CASE WHEN onduty_type NOT IN ( '4', '5' ) THEN 0.5 ELSE 0 END ) workdays2,
21 AS plan_workdays 
FROM
	attendance_daily 
WHERE
	attdate>=date_sub( date_sub(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL extract( DAY FROM CURRENT_DATE )- 1 DAY ), INTERVAL 1 MONTH ) 
GROUP BY
	usercode,
	date_format( attdate, '%Y-%m-01' )

SELECT
usercode,
date_format( attdate, '%Y-%m-01' ) MONTH,
sum( CASE WHEN onduty_type = '1' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) latetimes,
sum( CASE WHEN offduty_type = '3' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) overtimes1,
sum( CASE WHEN onduty_type = '3' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) overtimes2,
sum( CASE WHEN offduty_type = '2' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) leavetimes,
sum( absenceDay ) AS absencetimes,
sum( lateTime ) AS lateduration,
sum( overtimeTime ) AS overtimelength,
sum( leaveEarlyTime ) AS leavetduration,
sum( CASE WHEN offduty_type NOT IN ( '4', '5' ) THEN 0.5 ELSE 0 END ) workdays1,
sum( CASE WHEN onduty_type NOT IN ( '4', '5' ) THEN 0.5 ELSE 0 END ) workdays2,
21 AS plan_workdays 
FROM
	attendance_daily 
WHERE
	attdate>=date_sub( date_sub(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL extract( DAY FROM CURRENT_DATE )- 1 DAY ), INTERVAL 0 MONTH ) 
GROUP BY
	usercode,
	date_format( attdate, '%Y-%m-01' )
